{"tid":695492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 貨Van被爆窗偷腰包　送貨工成份糧冇晒","createTime":"2018-06-09T08:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T16:20:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a9684a98b6d462d656c6f922e6c75213da6e6c89","tid":695492,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T08:46:52.000Z","msg":"今日（9日）清晨5時許，一名送貨男工駕駛密斗貨車，停泊於油麻地窩打老道17號近東方街對開後，據稱因為趕著為茶餐龐送貨，急忙下將載有約1.5萬元薪金、銀包及一部手機的腰包遺於車內。<br />\n<br />\n僅僅約5分鐘後，男事主折返時，赫見貨車車窗被人扑爆，裝有全副薪金的腰包不翼而飛，大驚報警。警方事後於附近一帶兜截無果，正追緝賊人歸案。事後男事主憶述落車時已見有可疑南亞人士在旁徘徊，懷疑是他們所為，慨嘆自己才剛剛出糧，準備稍後入數，結果倒霉「破財」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1524896/org/5e55e3bca49dae103f51de2a03fcdbd9.jpg/KDkMhI-OG7OVpbqDeki1sTKFAR7UsNtx7H2Zv-x9mb8?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1524896%2Forg%2F5e55e3bca49dae103f51de2a03fcdbd9.jpg%2FKDkMhI-OG7OVpbqDeki1sTKFAR7UsNtx7H2Zv-x9mb8%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=24e4b706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/197366/%E8%B2%A8van%E8%A2%AB%E7%88%86%E7%AA%97%E5%81%B7%E8%85%B0%E5%8C%85-%E9%80%81%E8%B2%A8%E5%B7%A5%E6%88%90%E4%BB%BD%E7%B3%A7%E5%86%87%E6%99%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F197366%2F%25E8%25B2%25A8van%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%25AA%2597%25E5%2581%25B7%25E8%2585%25B0%25E5%258C%2585-%25E9%2580%2581%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E7%25B3%25A7%25E5%2586%2587%25E6%2599%2592&d=RrjgMgINASLqsOeJ4VYgWNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=b1c9765a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/197366/%E8%B2%A8van%E8%A2%AB%E7%88%86%E7%AA%97%E5%81%B7%E8%85%B0%E5%8C%85-%E9%80%81%E8%B2%A8%E5%B7%A5%E6%88%90%E4%BB%BD%E7%B3%A7%E5%86%87%E6%99%92</a>"},{"pid":"77cfd784e4676421b186bc50014a889bb57c5a8e","tid":695492,"uid":37501,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T08:54:49.000Z","ms